ygData.subject: Re: whops!didn't knew someone wrote that already!
ygData.msgSnippet: Druids get the personal teleportation around the world, and I believe they get group teleportation around the world.  But they do not get teleportation spells
ygData.messageBody:
Druids get the personal teleportation around the world, and I believe they
get group teleportation around the world. But they do not get teleportation
spells to another plane.

Tandayen, Dark Elf Wizard
